title: We Were Happy (Taylor's Version) (From The Vault)
description:
Taylor Swift brought in a partner for this song.. Her buddy Keith Urban! What is this song about? And why did she choose Keith for a couple of her vault songs? Amy, Ana, Lacey and Nick break this song down.. and someone has a legit breakdown. Stick around for the outtakes if you want to hear it!
What did we miss? Which album should we break down next? Let us know!
